---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About" description="Goutham Madhadi — Director of Digital Quality and Data Integrity at Beam Therapeutics.">
  <div class="about">
    <div class="about-header">
      <h1>About</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="about-body">
      <p>
        I'm <strong>Goutham Madhadi</strong>, Director of Digital Quality &amp; Data Integrity at
        <a href="https://beamtx.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Beam Therapeutics</a> — a
        biotech company pioneering base editing for genetic medicines.
      </p>

      <p>
        My work sits at the intersection of regulated quality systems, data governance, and modern
        software engineering. I lead data integrity programs across GxP systems — from LIMS and ELN
        platforms to manufacturing execution and BLA submissions.
      </p>

      <h2>What I work on</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>FDA 21 CFR Part 11 compliance and audit trail integrity</li>
        <li>ALCOA+ data quality frameworks for clinical and manufacturing data</li>
        <li>BLA (Biologics License Application) submissions and data packages</li>
        <li>GxP system validation, CSV, and computerized system compliance</li>
        <li>AI-assisted tools for quality monitoring and anomaly detection</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>This site</h2>
      <p>
        I write here about data integrity in regulated biotech, practical AI tooling for GxP
        environments, and anything else I find worth publishing. Opinions are my own.
      </p>

      <h2>Background</h2>
      <p>
        Before Beam, I built quality and data systems across pharma and biotech. Over the years
        I've developed a strong interest in applying software automation — particularly AI — to
        the compliance and data quality problems that regulated industries have historically
        solved with paper and spreadsheets.
      </p>

      <p>
        Outside of work, I'm a quantitative trader with a focus on options flow intelligence
        and momentum signals. I build my own tools — none of this is financial advice.
      </p>

      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>
        Email me at <a href="mailto:goutham@madhadi.com">goutham@madhadi.com</a>. I'm open to
        conversations about data integrity, GxP systems, AI in regulated industries, or anything
        on this site.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .about-body {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .about-body p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-body h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .about-body ul {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .about-body li {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    color: #d4d4d8;
  }

  .about-body strong { color: var(--text); }

  .about-body a {
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
</style>
